Using LKLUG CVS
---------------

Using PServer
-------------

o Yet to come ...

Using SSH
---------

o Set CVS_RSH to ssh

  On bash/sh

    export CVS_RSH=ssh

  On csh

    setenv CVS_RSH ssh

o Checkout the source

    cvs -d :ext:cvs.linux.lk:/cvs checkout sinhala

o Do the changes

o If you don't have write access, do a

    cvs diff -u [file]

  and send the output.  If you have write access

    cvs commit

o To add new text files:

    cvs add [file ...]
	cvs commit

o To add new binary files (images, etc)

    cvs add -kb [file ...]
	cvs commit

o To remove files:

    rm [file ...]
	cvs remove [file ...]
	cvs commit

